  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Drought affected households</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project is expected to alleviate suffering of drought affected marginal agricultural communities in the Mutha, Mutomo, and Yatta Divisions of Kitui District. The main areas of the project interventions will include: increasing target communities access to adequate and safe water for domestic uses, improving the overall management of the existing water sources, roll out of hygiene promotion program, and increasing water storage capacity for schools.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">improvement and rehabilitation of 13 water sources, training water and sanitation committees, promotion of point of use water treatment.</narrative>
  </description>
